item.title: CVE-2018-3881|2024-08-05T04:57:24.416Z -- focalscope -- focalscope
item.description: An exploitable unauthenticated XML external injection vulnerability was identified in FocalScope v2416. A unauthenticated attacker could submit a specially crafted web request to FocalScope's server that could cause an XXE, and potentially result in data compromise.
